==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Daman
<hw>Da"man</hw> <pr>(d⟦aum⟧"m⟦adot⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small herbivorous mammal of the genus
<gen>Hyrax</gen>. The species found in Palestine and Syria is <spn>Hyrax
Syriacus</spn>; that of Northern Africa is <spn>Hyrax Brucei</spn>; --
called also <altname>ashkoko</altname>, <altname>dassy</altname>, and
<altname>rock rabbit</altname>. See <er>Cony</er>, and
<er>Hyrax</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Damar</ent>⟦br⟧
